{"id":15357,"date":"2022-12-31T04:10:59","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:10:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:10:59","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:10:59","slug":"suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-2\/","title":{"rendered":"SUV \u0111i\u1ec7n Toyota bZ4X l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft Vi\u1ec7t Nam"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>M\u1eabu xe g\u1ea7m cao thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022, ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Toyota RAV4.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy lazy-blur\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1.jpg\" title=\"suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam-1.jpg 1200w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022, Toyota tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y bZ4X \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.  bZ4X Concept l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ra th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4\/2021, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 10 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ch\u1eef \u201cbZ\u201d trong t\u00ean xe c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cbeyond zero\u201d v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd xe kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.  Toyota c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u t\u00ean t\u1eeb bZ1X \u0111\u1ebfn bZ5X, v\u00e0 bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1eef \u201cX\u201d \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ed1n b\u00e1nh.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2022, Toyota tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y bZ4X \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trang tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.  bZ4X Concept l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ra th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4\/2021, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 10 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ch\u1eef \u201cbZ\u201d trong t\u00ean xe c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cbeyond zero\u201d v\u1edbi h\u00e0m \u00fd xe kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.  Toyota c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u t\u00ean t\u1eeb bZ1X \u0111\u1ebfn bZ5X, v\u00e0 bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1eef \u201cX\u201d \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ed1n b\u00e1nh.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" class=\"lazy lazy-blur\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672453445_721_suv-dien-toyota-bz4x-lan-dau-ra-mat-viet-nam.jpg\" title=\"167